_sText:
I made this map a little while ago for a mapping contest the Paradise Bunnyhop community was having as a quick example for some new mappers entering the contest.

This map was originally created for CS:GO but I decided to port it over to source. It is short, only 3 stages, and meant for speed running really.

Sorry, it has nothing to do with Sanic. I should probably change the name.

Thank you for checking out my map and feel free to leave any comments and such.
